<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<title>PICTORICAL</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h1>Blacklist Your Flickr Username From These Slideshows</h1>
		{% if username %}
        	<h2>"{{ username }}" has been blacklisted.</h2>
      	{% else %}
      		<p>The User ID we find for your username will be added to the blacklist that this application uses when vetting photos for display.
      		Once you have added yourself to the blacklist, you may go to the site's main page and refresh your browser, and you will
      		have the latest blacklist loaded, causing your photos to be exempted.</p>
	      	{% if error %}
	      		<p class="error">{{ error }}</p>
	      	{% endif %}
		    <form method="post">
		      <label for="user">Flickr Username</label>
		      <input type="text" name="user" size="30"/>
		      <input type="submit" value="Add To Blacklist">
		    </form>
		{% endif %}
	</body>
</html>